{"tid":2413346,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高先電影　業界先行　《狂舞派3》恢復港產片全用廣東話字幕傳統","createTime":"2021-02-18T15:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T18:01:30.000Z","uid":261647,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9d66ff6f451beea07ec2c5b58c202a47bfa13a8f","tid":2413346,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:29:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5302&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69BnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=aec7d73c\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5302</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/狂舞派3.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F%E7%8B%82%E8%88%9E%E6%B4%BE3.png%3Fw%3D1200%26ssl%3D1&h=d430c9fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日（18號）喺政府放寬限聚令下，戲院都終於開返，備受注目嘅本地電影《狂舞派3》久候多時都喺今日首映。製片商高先電影總經理曾麗芬透露，今次電影係有個有趣設定：「我哋會全用廣東話字幕。」<br />\n<br />\n佢又話：「其實早喺80年代港產片都係用廣東話字幕，今次我哋更搵到一間專門研究廣東話嘅團體幫手校對。」但就未有透露係邊個團體幫手校對。<br />\n<br />\n《狂舞派3》係劇情舞蹈片，由黃修平執導，今集就講咗好多本地rap文化。喺預告片中，睇到入邊有好多廣東話rap嘅內容，而當中用全廣東話字幕就好幫到觀眾去理解唱詞內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3GDBwbkwLZY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3GDBwbkwLZY&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69BnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=24490930\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3GDBwbkwLZY</a><br />\n<br />\n原本預定喺上年聖誕，但由於政府因疫情閂戲院，延期到今日（18號）上映。"},{"pid":"aa1f2404e9255eee5c24f1042a52ec84c0ba9357","tid":2413346,"uid":3406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f305cb19a951ceca41d0477e4330f128a4f7d8e9","tid":2413346,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score